  <summary date="2018-12-11T21:52:02Z" status="Introduced in Senate">National Flood Insurance Program Extension Act of 2018

This bill amends the National Flood Insurance Act of 1968 to reauthorize the National Flood Insurance Program through December 7, 2018.

The bill shall take effect as if it had been enacted on November 30, 2018.</summary>
